                    <WebAddress>https://www.fda.gov/animal-veterinary/safety-health/recalls-withdrawals</WebAddress>
                </FooterDetails>
                <Header>Animal and Veterinary Recalls</Header>
                <Paragraph>The FDA posts animal and veterinary recall information—brand name, date of recall, company name, product description, and the reason or problem—on its website.</Paragraph>
            </EntitySourceOfInformation>
            <EntitySourceOfInformation EntitySourceOfInformationId="775" SortOrder="2">
                <FooterDetails>
