                    <WebAddress>https://www.fda.gov/consumers/free-publications-women/birth-control-chart</WebAddress>
                </FooterDetails>
                <Header>Birth Control</Header>
                <Paragraph>The FDA has posted a birth control chart that contains information about different options for avoiding pregnancy.</Paragraph>
            </EntitySourceOfInformation>
