                </FooterDetails>
                <Header>Career Opportunities</Header>
                <Paragraph>The FDA relies on attorneys, biologists, chemists, consumer safety officers, engineers, information technology specialists, medical officers, microbiologists, pharmacists, pharmacologists, statisticians, and other professionals, to carry out its mission.</Paragraph>
            </EntitySourceOfInformation>
